title: Episode 8 - Buddy Nielsen from Senses Fail
itunes:title: Episode 8 - Buddy Nielsen from Senses Fail
description:
In this episode I had a great conversation with Buddy Nielsen, the vocalist from Senses Fail about everything from his bands journey in and around the mainstream, being successful on your own terms and how he still keeps the excitement for new bands. This podcast is part of the Punknews network, visit punknews.org for all the latest news in independent music.
